reviewText: For a Greater Vision fanatic this DVD is like Heaven too me.  With the combination of a CD of same name it just makes it much better.
Excellent dvd so glad I have it, plays great. More than Satisfied.

If you are a fan of Greater Vision this DVD Is a must have for you.  Not only do we get a 1 hour concert from Gerald Rodney and Jason but we get a 1 hour reunion with Gerald Mark & Chris the original G.V.  They bring back memories for long time G.V. Fans. you will old hits like "On A Journey" "New Wine" and "He Is Mine". Any fan Of Greater Vision will love this DVD
